The paper discusses the trade-off between false accept and false reject errors in biometric authentication systems, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the encoding of biometric signals into secret keys, which involves information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of biometric signals such as images (cs.CV) and the comparison of different types of codes (cs.MM, cs.LG).
